[
    {
        "source_sentence": "壹輸盧迦論一卷",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "龍樹菩薩造",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後魏瞿曇留支雒陽譯",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "體自體無常，　　如是體無體；",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自體性無體，　　故說空無常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問曰：",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以何義故造此一偈論？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說何等義破何等人？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答曰：",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為讀誦者於廣大部生懈倦心，又為聰叡先已廣習無量諸論於如來法海義中思惟而生懈倦，於無常自體空不異義中生異相疑，為斷此疑故造斯論。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說何義者，今當說。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂一切法無常自體空，自體空不離無常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法自性自體空，是故無有常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸佛緣覺聲聞於空法中而得出離，非於諸行斷常法中而得解脫。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈言：",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「滅空住有體，　　則成於常見；",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若謂後時滅，　　則成於斷見。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」以此義故，說一切法自體空。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛緣覺聲聞羅漢，於此義中得利益故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "破何等人者，今當說。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有所得人離於諸行說有無常，則非正見。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無常離有為，無常則常，猶如虛空。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是者，則有為無為體無差別。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有為與無為合，無為合故則瓶不可破。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無為與有為合，有為合故則涅槃可壞。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不異者，則一切法不可破壞，如涅槃常，非緣生故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸行非因緣生，不異虛空涅槃者，則有為法不名無常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253a28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸行非因緣生、是無常者，則虛空涅槃不名為常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是者，則有為無為無有勝法。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無常離有為猶名無常者，則有為離常應名為常；",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但是事不然。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是者，何等修多羅中作如是說？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以何義說？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今所說以何義說？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今所說義不相應，非汝邪思之所能量，是故汝說非為正見。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人有所得，謂過去未來現在法自體成者，當知是人則非正見。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無因生見故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言未來體非因緣生自體成者，則現在法亦非因緣生自性體成，以未來現在自性平等無差別故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若性平等者，現在有法皆從緣生，未來法何故非緣生？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今此義為以修多羅說？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為依義說？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "說不相應則無理趣，若無理趣則不可信。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若未來法無因緣生自性成者，未來之法猶如虛空無有因緣，離因緣故非因緣生則無實未來體，無未來故現在過去亦無，現在過去無故三世無體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有體者，則是常見，無因生故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若佛弟子有所得見，則與外道迦毘羅等無差別。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此論非為迦毘羅、憂樓迦諸外道等，為汝等輩同見之人故造斯論。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "向說破何等人？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為令汝等有所得人斷除邪見故作斯論。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一輸盧迦偈句義今當釋。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈言自體性無常者，自體名有生，有法故名為體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有所得人於此法中心取為體，此法於陰界入中有聲緣轉，如說一體二體多體，如彼此人一二眾多各有自體故名自體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如地水火風堅濕熱動各有自性，如是各各自相自體，故言自體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有所得人謂生住滅同相者，是義不然，自體性無常故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253b28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼體名有所得人分別故生，是故離諸法無無常體，以自相無常故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如佛告比丘：",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切諸行皆悉無常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」以此說故，離法有無常自相者，是事不然。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若汝不了云何無常？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今當說。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈言如是體無體故，體無體者，汝所分別無常者，彼無常無體，是故體無體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性無體，故言無體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈言自體性無體者，離無體更無別體，故言自體無體。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若汝意謂離無體而有體者，是義不然，以汝此法非修多羅說故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若謂無體是自體者，是亦不然，以修多羅所不說故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊於何等修多羅中說如此法？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於佛世尊修多羅中都無此義，以非經說故不成就。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非大聖修多羅所說之義則不應信，是故非唯言說而得取證。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈言故說空無常者，如《調伏三蜜提經》中說，佛告三蜜提：",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「眼空、無常、無不動、無不壞、無不變。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性如是故。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳鼻舌身意亦復如是。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」世尊於此修多羅中說空、說無常，以是義故，知諸法空無常。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無常無體，是故諸法性自無體，則無體義成。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能如是入修多羅義，其義則成；",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不入修多羅，其義則壞。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以我所說入修多羅，其義則成。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故性自無體，其義成就。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一輸盧迦論一卷，凡諸法體性法物事有名異義同，是故或言體、或言性、或言法、或言有、或言物，莫不皆是有之差別。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正音云私婆婆，或譯為自體體，或譯為無法有法。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或譯為無自性性。",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "壹輸盧迦論一卷",
        "from": "T30n1573_001:0253c26_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]